<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Michał Okoń - Portfolio</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="zadanka/apple.png" type="image/png">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            --secondary-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
            --accent-color: #007AFF;
            --background-gradient: linear-gradient(45deg, #0a0a0a, #1a1a1a);
            --glass-bg: rgba(15, 15, 15, 0.65);
            --border-radius: 12px;
            --spacing: 1rem;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: var(--background-gradient);
            color: var(--primary-color);
            line-height: 1.6;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        .video-container {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            z-index: -1;
            opacity: 0.4;
        }

        video {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        header {
            padding: 1.5rem;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            top: 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .content-wrapper {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 100px 2rem 2rem;
        }

        .portfolio-card {
            background: var(--glass-bg);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            padding: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .portfolio-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .dropdown-container {
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .dropdown-list {
            position: absolute;
            right: 0;
            top: 100%;
            min-width: 240px;
            background: var(--glass-bg);
            backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            padding: 0.5rem 0;
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
            opacity: 0;
            visibility: hidden;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .dropdown-container:hover .dropdown-list {
            opacity: 1;
            visibility: visible;
        }

        .dropdown-list a {
            display: block;
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }

        .dropdown-list a:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            color: var(--primary-color);
            padding-left: 2rem;
        }

        .nav-link {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            margin-top: auto;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .video-container {
                display: none;
            }
            
            body {
                background: #0a0a0a;
            }
            
            .content-wrapper {
                padding: 80px 1rem 1rem;
            }
            
            .portfolio-card {
                padding: 1.5rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="video-container">
        <video autoplay muted loop>
            <source src="zadanka/apple.mp4" type="video/mp4">
        </video>
    </div>

    <header>
        <nav>
            <div class="dropdown-container">
                <button class="nav-link">
                    <i class="fas fa-folder-open"></i>
                    Moje projekty
                </button>
                <div class="dropdown-list">
                    <a href="zadanka/kotwice_auta.html">
                        <i class="fas fa-car"></i>
                        Artykuł o autach
                    </a>
                    <a href="zadanka/kotwice.html">
                        <i class="fas fa-anchor"></i>
                        Strona Kotwice
                    </a>
                    <a href="zadanka/herby.html">
                        <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                        Herby
                    </a>
                    <a href="zadanka/tabele.html">
                        <i class="fas fa-table"></i>
                        Tabele
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <div class="content-wrapper">
        <div class="portfolio-card">
            <h1>Michał Okoń</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Klasa 4D</p>
            <div class="contact-info">
                <p><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Michu2020o@gmail.com</p>
                <p><i class="fas fa-phone"></i> +48 123 456 789</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="portfolio-card">
            <h2>O mnie</h2>
            <p>Jestem uczniem klasy 4D pasjonującym się tworzeniem stron internetowych i nowymi technologiami. W moich projektach staram się łączyć funkcjonalność z nowoczesnym designem.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Michał Okoń | Wszelkie prawa zastrzeżone</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>